data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!! Nice family home located in the quiet community of Southwyck.  Gracious 2 story entry in this nice sized 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath with a 2 car garage. Home has a formal dining room which is great for hosting holiday parties and family dinners. Gorgeous kitchen with granite, stainless steel appliances with plenty of cabinet and counter top space with a Samsung touch screen refrigerator. Utility room adjoins the kitchen which has ample storage room and the washer and dryer are included. Spacious family room with a fireplace and recessed lighting that overflows into the breakfast area. Spacious family room that features a fireplace and recessed lighting. Light & bright primary bedroom with a large walk in closet, whirlpool tub and separate shower, and double sinks. Upstairs has 3 bedrooms and spacious game room with two niches for a home office space or build matching shelving. Great backyard with a wonderful Pergola. Home has energy saving Solar Panels. Some TLC is needed.
